{"tid":1355468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提防「守護馬鞍山居民小隊」 地區版白衫軍陸續面世","createTime":"2019-07-23T10:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:23:14.000Z","uid":47194,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d66778123d1befd1ddb38b0977b04d1f3cd6fc","tid":1355468,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"是日有報道 &quot;昨午成立的「守護馬鞍山居民小隊」，也於昨晚八時開始行動，在恆安邨邨口、馬鞍山廣場地下、港鐵大水坑站及烏溪沙站駐守，各處據點均有約五十人，並配備長傘等物資作防衞。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n本來以為「守護馬鞍山居民小隊」是麥潤培區議員搞出來的傑作，但將關鍵字輸入Google，就會得出驚人結果：除了星島系的1. 星島日報、2. 頭條日報、3. 巴士的報，就沒有任何關於這個「守護馬鞍山居民小隊」的消息，恐怕是親建制陣營(尤其親星島陣營)實行特區政府群眾鬥群眾策略，在馬鞍山搞出來的白衫軍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.lmgtfy.com/?q=%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.lmgtfy.com%2F%3Fq%3D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259E%258D%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWE5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=a9c29702\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.lmgtfy.com/?q=%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山居民、18區義士必須做好戰鬥準備，買定麵粉棍行山杖，迎接全港大亂鬥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f1d4951f0bef15130496260408f18d606215cf","tid":1355468,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ba7e59de60b93bce924ef670379cc4c742cfe2c","tid":1355468,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f5b1083d042e67791e33fb420eef18c09367cef9","tid":1355468,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"中聯辦洗地呀？"},{"pid":"997f9ec0b69c019072637a341cc7705aad0f7c8e","tid":1355468,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"佢地在明我地在暗 唔驚俾人偷襲咩？<img s